lead_paragraph: After nine people were killed in an earthquake on Thursday on the island of Kyushu, a more powerful temblor struck the same area, killing at least 23.

headline.print_headline: A Second Powerful Earthquake Strikes Japan

abstract: Magnitude 7.3 earthquake strikes Japanese island of Kyushu, killing at least 11 people.
